This paper discusses the initial access procedure in mmWave networks, which involves beamforming and communication protocols. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and signal processing, which are covered in cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses system-level issues and optimization, which are covered in cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
